#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-catalyst-module.md:1
msgid "Add VTK::catalyst module"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-catalyst-module.md:3
msgid ""
"VTK now has a new module called `VTK::catalyst` which is enabled with "
"VTK_ENABLE_CATALYST, It looks for an external Catalyst installation and "
"exposes catalyst's CMake functionality. Other VTK modules, such as `VTK::"
"IOCatalystConduit`, can now depend on `VTK::catalyst` instead of trying to "
"find the Catalyst package themselves."
msgstr ""
